",[61],{"type":20,"value":62},"Use-Case Diagramm",{"type":14,"tag":33,"props":64,"children":65},{},[66],{"type":20,"value":67},"Ein Use-Case-Diagramm hilft, die Interaktionen zwischen den Spielern und dem Spielsystem zu visualisieren. Für \"Terror Nightmare Towers\" umfasst unser Use-Case-Diagramm:",{"type":14,"tag":69,"props":70,"children":71},"ul",{},[72,84,94],{"type":14,"tag":73,"props":74,"children":75},"li",{},[76,82],{"type":14,"tag":77,"props":78,"children":79},"strong",{},[80],{"type":20,"value":81},"Spieleraktionen:",{"type":20,"value":83}," Bewegen, Bauen, Angreifen, Verteidigen, Power-Ups verwenden.",{"type":14,"tag":73,"props":85,"children":86},{},[87,92],{"type":14,"tag":77,"props":88,"children":89},{},[90],{"type":20,"value":91},"Systemreaktionen:",{"type":20,"value":93}," Spielbrett aktualisieren, Siegbedingungen überprüfen, Ereignisse auslösen.",{"type":14,"tag":73,"props":95,"children":96},{},[97,102],{"type":14,"tag":77,"props":98,"children":99},{},[100],{"type":20,"value":101},"Admin-Aktionen:",{"type":20,"value":103}," Spiel einrichten, Spieler verwalten, Regeln anpassen.",{"type":14,"tag":39,"props":105,"children":106},{},[],{"type":14,"tag":43,"props":108,"children":110},{"id":109},"strukturplan",[111],{"type":20,"value":112},"Strukturplan",{"type":14,"tag":33,"props":114,"children":115},{},[116],{"type":20,"value":117},"Unser Strukturplan skizziert die Hauptkomponenten des Spiels und deren Interaktionen. Er umfasst:",{"type":14,"tag":69,"props":119,"children":120},{},[121,131,141,151,161],{"type":14,"tag":73,"props":122,"children":123},{},[124,129],{"type":14,"tag":77,"props":125,"children":126},{},[127],{"type":20,"value":128},"Spielbrett:",{"type":20,"value":130}," Das physische Layout, auf dem das Spiel gespielt wird.",{"type":14,"tag":73,"props":132,"children":133},{},[134,139],{"type":14,"tag":77,"props":135,"children":136},{},[137],{"type":20,"value":138},"Spielerfiguren:",{"type":20,"value":140}," Spielfiguren, die jeden Spieler auf dem Brett repräsentieren.",{"type":14,"tag":73,"props":142,"children":143},{},[144,149],{"type":14,"tag":77,"props":145,"children":146},{},[147],{"type":20,"value":148},"Karten und Power-Ups:",{"type":20,"value":150}," Spezielle Gegenstände, die strategische Vorteile bieten.",{"type":14,"tag":73,"props":152,"children":153},{},[154,159],{"type":14,"tag":77,"props":155,"children":156},{},[157],{"type":20,"value":158},"Regel-Engine:",{"type":20,"value":160}," Die Kernlogik, die die Spielregeln und -mechaniken durchsetzt.",{"type":14,"tag":73,"props":162,"children":163},{},[164,169],{"type":14,"tag":77,"props":165,"children":166},{},[167],{"type":20,"value":168},"Punktestand-Verfolger:",{"type":20,"value":170}," Ein System, das die Punktestände und den Spielverlauf verfolgt.",{"type":14,"tag":39,"props":172,"children":173},{},[],{"type":14,"tag":43,"props":175,"children":177},{"id":176},"gantt-diagramm",[178],{"type":20,"value":179},"Gantt Diagramm",{"type":14,"tag":33,"props":181,"children":182},{},[183],{"type":20,"value":184},"Um unser Projekt im Zeitplan zu halten, haben wir ein Gantt-Diagramm erstellt, das unseren Zeitplan detailliert:",{"type":14,"tag":69,"props":186,"children":187},{},[188,198,208,218,228],{"type":14,"tag":73,"props":189,"children":190},{},[191,196],{"type":14,"tag":77,"props":192,"children":193},{},[194],{"type":20,"value":195},"Konzeptentwicklung:",{"type":20,"value":197}," 1. Jan - 31. Jan",{"type":14,"tag":73,"props":199,"children":200},{},[201,206],{"type":14,"tag":77,"props":202,"children":203},{},[204],{"type":20,"value":205},"Designphase:",{"type":20,"value":207}," 1. Feb - 15. Mär",{"type":14,"tag":73,"props":209,"children":210},{},[211,216],{"type":14,"tag":77,"props":212,"children":213},{},[214],{"type":20,"value":215},"Implementierung:",{"type":20,"value":217}," 16. Mär - 30. Jun",{"type":14,"tag":73,"props":219,"children":220},{},[221,226],{"type":14,"tag":77,"props":222,"children":223},{},[224],{"type":20,"value":225},"Testen und Verfeinern:",{"type":20,"value":227}," 1. Jul - 31. Aug",{"type":14,"tag":73,"props":229,"children":230},{},[231,236],{"type":14,"tag":77,"props":232,"children":233},{},[234],{"type":20,"value":235},"Startvorbereitung:",{"type":20,"value":237}," 1. Sep - 30. Sep",{"type":14,"tag":39,"props":239,"children":240},{},[],{"type":14,"tag":43,"props":242,"children":244},{"id":243},"visuals-konzept",[245],{"type":20,"value":246},"Visuals & Konzept",{"type":14,"tag":33,"props":248,"children":249},{},[250],{"type":20,"value":251},"Unser Spiel zeichnet sich durch einen einzigartigen visuellen Stil und thematische Vielfalt aus. Hier ist eine Übersicht unseres Ansatzes:",{"type":14,"tag":69,"props":253,"children":254},{},[255,265,275],{"type":14,"tag":73,"props":256,"children":257},{},[258,263],{"type":14,"tag":77,"props":259,"children":260},{},[261],{"type":20,"value":262},"Pixel Stil:",{"type":20,"value":264}," Die Grafik des Spiels wird in Pixel-Art gehalten, was ihm einen nostalgischen, aber modernen Touch verleiht.",{"type":14,"tag":73,"props":266,"children":267},{},[268,273],{"type":14,"tag":77,"props":269,"children":270},{},[271],{"type":20,"value":272},"2,5D Sicht:",{"type":20,"value":274}," Wir verwenden eine 2,5D-Perspektive, um dem Spielbrett Tiefe zu verleihen und das visuelle Erlebnis zu verbessern, ohne die Komplexität eines vollständigen 3D-Designs.",{"type":14,"tag":73,"props":276,"children":277},{},[278,283],{"type":14,"tag":77,"props":279,"children":280},{},[281],{"type":20,"value":282},"Mehrere Themes:",{"type":20,"value":284}," Das Spiel wird verschiedene Themen umfassen, wie Gothic Horror, Sci-Fi und Fantasy, jedes mit einzigartigen Visuals und Spielmechaniken.",{"type":14,"tag":39,"props":286,"children":287},{},[],{"type":14,"tag":43,"props":289,"children":291},{"id":290},"architektur",[292],{"type":20,"value":293},"Architektur",{"type":14,"tag":33,"props":295,"children":296},{},[297],{"type":20,"value":298},"Wir haben das Model-View-Controller (MVC) Muster gewählt, um die Softwarearchitektur unseres Spiels zu strukturieren:",{"type":14,"tag":69,"props":300,"children":301},{},[302,312,322],{"type":14,"tag":73,"props":303,"children":304},{},[305,310],{"type":14,"tag":77,"props":306,"children":307},{},[308],{"type":20,"value":309},"Model:",{"type":20,"value":311}," Verwaltet die Spieldaten, -logik und -regeln. Dies umfasst den Spielbrettzustand, die Spielerpositionen und die Punkteverfolgung.",{"type":14,"tag":73,"props":313,"children":314},{},[315,320],{"type":14,"tag":77,"props":316,"children":317},{},[318],{"type":20,"value":319},"View:",{"type":20,"value":321}," Handhabt die visuelle Darstellung des Spiels. Dies umfasst das 2,5D-Brett, die Spielerfiguren und Animationen.",{"type":14,"tag":73,"props":323,"children":324},{},[325,330],{"type":14,"tag":77,"props":326,"children":327},{},[328],{"type":20,"value":329},"Controller:",{"type":20,"value":331}," Verwaltet Benutzereingaben und -interaktionen. Es verarbeitet Spieleraktionen und aktualisiert das Modell und die Ansicht entsprechend.",{"type":14,"tag":33,"props":333,"children":334},{},[335],{"type":20,"value":336},"Dieses Architekturmodell sorgt für eine klare Trennung der Verantwortlichkeiten und erleichtert die Entwicklung, das Testen und die Wartung des Spiels.",{"type":14,"tag":39,"props":338,"children":339},{},[],{"type":14,"tag":43,"props":341,"children":343},{"id":342},"schlussfolgerung",[344],{"type":20,"value":345},"Schlussfolgerung",{"type":14,"tag":33,"props":347,"children":348},{},[349],{"type":20,"value":350},"Wir sind begeistert von der Entwicklung von \"Terror Nightmare Towers\" und können es kaum erwarten, Ihnen weitere Updates zu geben. Bleiben Sie dran für weitere Einblicke in unseren Spieldesignprozess, die Entwicklung der visuellen Kunst und einen Blick hinter die Kulissen unseres Fortschritts!",{"type":14,"tag":39,"props":352,"children":353},{},[],{"type":14,"tag":33,"props":355,"children":356},{},[357],{"type":20,"value":358},"Vielen Dank, dass Sie unseren Weg begleiten. Bis zum nächsten Mal!",{"type":14,"tag":33,"props":360,"children":361},{},[362],{"type":14,"tag":27,"props":363,"children":364},{},[365],{"type":20,"value":366},"Nick Schumacher",{"title":7,"searchDepth":368,"depth":368,"links":369},2,[370,371,372,373,374,375,376],{"id":45,"depth":368,"text":48},{"id":59,"depth":368,"text":62},{"id":109,"depth":368,"text":112},{"id":176,"depth":368,"text":179},{"id":243,"depth":368,"text":246},{"id":290,"depth":368,"text":293},{"id":342,"depth":368,"text":345},"markdown","content:projekte:tnt.md","content","projekte/tnt.md","md",1719235696712]